spec_data.Name: emacs-auto-complete-el
spec_data.Description:
This package contains the elisp source files for Auto Complete Mode
under GNU Emacs. You do not need to install this package to run
Auto Complete Mode. Install the emacs-auto-complete package to use
Auto Complete Mode with GNU Emacs.
